{"tid":1843434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省實施公共場所必須戴口罩措施　違者依法處理","createTime":"2020-01-26T08:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:39:53.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ef99f71c2f7d2bb39fbf215353fb5406e9945138","tid":1843434,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"廣東省實施公共場所必須戴口罩措施　違者依法處理<br />\n<br />\n廣東省為防新型冠狀病毒疫情擴散，決定即日起全省公共場所，實施佩戴口罩措施。通告要求民眾在酒店、卡啦OK、體育館、步行街、商場、公共交通等人群聚集的地方戴上口罩，各公共場所經營者應該要求進入場所的人戴口罩，並在入口設置提示，勸阻未佩戴口罩人士，不聽勸阻的人將依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-26 15:42:40"},{"pid":"680f4ff29585f84bf33cf4e159731e8c2398f708","tid":1843434,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"林鄭：我會繼續上訴禁蒙面法"},{"pid":"0438ff624cb9355d758984cbd76366f470bfdc04","tid":1843434,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"香港仲衰過支那"},{"pid":"9c03bfae29defb395a96ca4ece2dddee28e80a3b","tid":1843434,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374aa4dc72466e813596177e0716d31e9eb35f1f","tid":1843434,"uid":116194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"冇口罩點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc13d0cf5b3875b0b03e76e2adbc60da21d18e6c","tid":1843434,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"點解香港唔可以用緊急法進戴口罩法???<br />\n上次都係一日就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n點解? 點解? 點解?<br />\n黑人問號"},{"pid":"76c91bcbf1305ac8e03fcfdfb8a6827112243e2c","tid":1843434,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"中國人需要管的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc0a5ca0a374bae15d20bab3cdb3b0a4d1a3680","tid":1843434,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":